data.description: This diamond is no longer in the rough completely renovated and pride of ownership shows through out your future home. Brand new architectural roof, updated double pane windows, all new hardie plank siding and paint, new garage door, updated plumbing, fully  fenced yard thats ready for you to enjoy. Interior boasts many modern updates such as new soft close kitchen cabinets and countertops, tile in wet areas and premium laminate flooring through out the home, tastefully remodeled bathrooms and much more. This home features 2 master bedrooms both with walk-in closets.  Conveniently located within walking distance to the mall, restaurants and other shopping centers. This one is a must see !!
